Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能聽到我說話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞迪雷克出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能馬上過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要史雷的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞迪雷克附近又出現了龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎！艾莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:01:05.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悲しみに囚われた魂達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:01:05.58,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}為悲傷所困的靈魂們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:15.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}終わらない憎しみが叫びだす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:15.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}因無盡的憎恨而呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:20.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}迷いの森を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:20.67,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}穿過迷惘的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:24.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}世界照らしに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:24.35,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們將去照亮世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:29.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絶望抱きしめるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:29.74,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}會去擁抱絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:34.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}諦めていない証
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:34.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}說明還未放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:40.34,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}孤独超えたら信じあえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:40.34,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}當我們跨越孤獨便可互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:43.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絆離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:43.21,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要放開這份情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:48.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望という眩しい重さに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:48.03,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望炫目而又沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:53.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}負けない情熱この手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:53.73,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}手中握有不被壓倒的熱誠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:02:00.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想い  光へ  何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:02:00.29,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}思念化作光芒 無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:04.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}命尽き果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:04.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}直至生命耗盡
